# Adaptive-Agentic-RAG-Langgraph

Agentic + Adaptive RAG built from scratch with LangGraph:
- Router (vectorstore vs web)
- Document grading (relevance)
- Web search tool (Tavily)
- Answer grounding + usefulness graders
- Auto-correction loops (regenerate / fallback)

## Setup
1) Create `.env` 
2) Install dependencies


